### Handy variables

### Volume and brightness steps
    set $volume_step 5
    set $brightness_step 4

### Swaylock timeout
    set $lock_timer 120
    set $black_screen_delay 30
    set $suspend_delay 30

### Wallpaper
    set $wallpaper "$HOME/Pictures/.wallpaper"
    set $lock_bg "$HOME/Pictures/.screensaver"
